doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
  body
    h1
      a(href='/member') 회원관리
    ul
      each member in members
        li
          a(href='/member/'+member.phone)= member.phone
    artcle
      if member
        h2 회원정보
        p
        ='ID= '+member.ID
        p
        ='전화번호= '+member.phone
        p
        ='포인트= '+member.point
        form(action='/member/'+member.phone+'/addpoint' method='get')
          p
            input(type='submit' value='포인트적립')
      else
        h2 Welcome
        | 회원정보를 누르면 편집할 수 있습니다.
    ul
      li
        a(href='/member/add') 회원추가
        if member
          li
            a(href='/member/'+member.phone+'/edit') edit
          li
            a(href='/member/'+member.phone+'/delete') delete
